{"tid":496672,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(請賜教) 狗屎收集箱 同 狗主","createTime":"2017-12-12T02:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T02:19:08.000Z","uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64dc3ffd2c464cd71b670ba6cd0836e70d50268d","tid":496672,"uid":46781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:19:08.000Z","msg":"有人話狗主見到啲箱就會覺得嗰啲位可以屙屎， 放狗時就會帶狗去嗰個位屙屎屙尿，所以應該要移走啲狗屎筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尤其係啲無咩風嘅位，例如天橋同隊隧道，陣狗尿味真係壓到仆街<br />\n<br />\n通常見啲狗主攞住枝水射幾滴水就走， 有用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果移走啲筒，又係咪真係有用？ <br />\n係咪狗主就唔會俾隻狗喺嗰度屙屎屙尿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢樣野諗咗好撚耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n明明養貓就最好，又唔影響人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}